Yeesu wi'imo, “E mi wi'umaa goonga, walaa baawayɗo natta Laamu Allah sey to ɗum fuɗɗitii ɗum danyiimo.”
Nikoodimus ƴamimo wi'i, “No neɗɗo mawɗo danyitirtee? Ɗum waɗataako o so''o nder reedu maduujo maako ɗum fuɗɗita ɗum danyamo ɗiɗaɓum.”
Yeesu wi'imo, “E mi wi'umaa goonga, walaa baawayɗo natta Laamu Allah sey ni to ndiyam e Ruuhu Allah danyiimo.
Ko neɗɗo danyi ɗum neɗɗo, ammaa ko Ruuhu danyi ɗum ruuhu.
Taa' hayɗin ngam mi wi'iima doole ɗum fuɗɗita ɗum danyumaa.
Hendu e wisa to yiɗiri, a nana sonnyo mayru, ammaa a andaa to ndu ƴiwoyi koo to ndu yahata. Non maa ɗum wontindiri e koo moye mo Ruuhu Allah danyi.”
