Wonduɓe e am ngi'i jayngol ngol, ammaa ɓe nanaayi hononde metanayɗoyam on.
Wonduɓe e am njoganiiyam juuɗe haa nder gariiri Dimasku, ngam jayngol ngol wumniiyam.
“Nder gariiri ndin e woodi goɗɗo neɗɗo bi'eteeɗo Hanaaniya, kuloowo Joomiraawo, tokkuɗo Attawra, mo Yahuudanko'en jooɗiiɓe ton fuu manata.
