Malaa'ika'en fuu e ndarii pilii jooɗorgal laamu ngal e mawɓe ɓen ɗon e tagaaɗum nayum gooduɗum yonki ɗum ɗon. Ɓe fuu ɓe njani ɓe mawnini Allah.
E ɓe mbi'a, “Aamin! Mantuki, e teddungal, e faamu, e yettoore, e mangu, e bawɗe, e sembe tabbita to Allah meeɗen haa abadaa abadin! Aamin.”
Sey go'oto nder mawɓe ɓen ɗon ƴamiyam wi'i, “Ɗum ɓeye ɓe'e yimɓe ɓorniiɓe kolte daneeje? Nden daga toye ɓe ƴiwoyi?”
Sey mbiimoomi, “Mi andaa, mawɗo. An a andi.” Sey o wi'iyam, “Ɓe'e yimɓe kamɓe ƴiwoyi daga nder torra kalluka. Ɓe laɓɓiniri kolte maɓɓe e ƴiiƴam Karoori ndin ɗe ndanni tar.
