Nde malaa'ikaajo ɗiɗaɓo duudi luwal muuɗum, sey ɗum hubii goɗɗum nder maayo nanduɗum e hocceere mawnde e ɗum nyaama hiite. Daga ɗon sendere go'o nder cende tati ɗe maayo ngon warti ƴiiƴam.
Nden sendere go'o nder cende tati ɗe marle maayo ngon mbaati, nden sendere go'o nder cende tati ɗe komiije gonɗe ɗon kalki.
Nde malaa'ikaajo tataɓo duudi luwal muuɗum, sey wonde hoodere yanoyi daga dow e nde nyaama hiite bo yawre nde ɗum yardata nyaaki. Nde yani dow sendere go'o nder cende tati ɗe canɗi e to ndiyam ɓuliroyta.
Inde hoodere nden “Kaɗɗum.” Sey sendere go'o nder cende tati ɗe ndiyam warti kaɗɗam. Yimɓe ɗuɗɓe nde njari ndiyam ɗam ɓe maayi ngam ɗam wartii kaɗɗam.
